name: Rare Poewk
description: The debate rages on as to whether Poewk's head features a mask or a face - the Rare of the species has an equally disquieting countenance. Everything about the Rare Poewk extols a return to nature: a covering of crimson feathers, the twisting, bending pipes encircled around it, the dirt-patch it insists upon for its clawed foot-stomping performance.
polarity: Negative from: Rare Bona-Petite, Negative toward: Rare Maulch, Positive from: Rare Brump, Positive toward: Rare Tympa
